   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting" image="QW_35.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-a" mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Do you remember the <FONT color=#a82424>Dried Marissa Spring</FONT>? There exists strange rocks called <FONT color=#a82424>Rune Shards</FONT>. I believe there will be evidence of experiments ancient people had done over the ruins.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-b" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>I believe especially the <FONT color=#a82424>Rune Shards</FONT> are closely related to <FONT color=#a82424>the accident</FONT>. Nobody knows for sure what had happened over there. Some speculations include explosions, internal fight between the ancient people, etc..</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-c" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>Weapon? What kind of weapon?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>But many researchers think that happened while making some kind of a <FONT color=#a82424>weapon</FONT>. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Stas goes over his records and contemplates on some idea)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-d" mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>Hard to believe.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>I believe that's the Black Dragon. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Stas carefully looks around)</FONT> …Shh! It's just a hypothesis. As I said before, from speculation, the Black Dragon from <FONT color=#a82424>50 years ago</FONT> is close to some sort of a <FONT color=#a82424>manmade creature</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-e" mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>Alright</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>I know it's a bit farfetched. But I continue to study to find the <FONT color=#a82424>evidence</FONT>.<BR>Will you help me?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-accepting-acceptted" mid="16"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Catastrophic Rain IV$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-1" image="QW_35.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas${action:talk}<BR>Then hurry to the <FONT color=#a82424>Dried Marissa Spring</FONT> and collect about 5 <FONT color=#a82424>Rune Shards</FONT>.<BR>From that, my hypothesis could turn into conviction.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-a" mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>(Stas carefully looks around)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>The Royal Castle is trying to cover up the battle with the monster. But as I have fought in the battle <FONT color=#a82424>50 years ago</FONT>, I hear things from people. I knew you also fought in the recent battle.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-b" mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas${action:talk}<BR>I saw it 50 years ago. Royal Knight <FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT> betraying us… I couldn't believe my eyes.<BR> But that incident was covered up and everyone considers him as a <FONT color=#a82424>Hero</FONT>? In that sense, I couldn't tell the truth.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-c" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>People needed a hero after war.<BR>But, the shape of the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT>, or the contaminated blood coming out from him when he was injured… I can't get the out of my head. I've seen it before.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-d" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>I was studying on the <FONT color=#a82424>Catastrophic Rain</FONT> when I was a junior researcher. That was it.<BR>But during the chaos, <FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT>vanished, and I searched all sorts of materials. So I sometimes was misunderstood as a <FONT color=#a82424>dragon follower</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-e" mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>Hypothesis?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>But I received a top that the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT> that appeared recently was in fact, <FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT>. He took control of the Black Dragon's jewel and borrowing the ancient power, became the Black Dragon. <BR>Then, I was able to found my hypothesis.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-f" mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>Then, the accident that occurred in the ancient times?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>As I said before, the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT> from 50 years ago might also be manmade.<BR>Like Velskud, that Black Dragon from 50 years ago, might have been made a long time ago with the help of <FONT color=#a82424>ancient people</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-g" mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>Wow… Amazing story.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Indeed. I believe it's due to that <FONT color=#a82424>experiment</FONT>.<BR>Also, they say we eliminated the Black Dragon, but since we didn't inflict as much damage as last time, it might still be alive.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-g" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-h" mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>(Stas searched his pocket)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Is every dragon made? I'm not sure. What would a person need to become a dragon after acquiring the <FONT color=#a82424>jewel</FONT>. Why did the ancient experiment left such a devastating <FONT color=#a82424>ruins</FONT>… Now is the time to study that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-i" mid="36"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-i" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas${action:talk}<BR>After I told you everything, I feel much better!<BR>Thanks for everything. Goodbye.</html>]]></talk_question>
